{"word":"καθυπέρτερος","slug":"καθυπέρτερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καθυπέρτερος</b></el> <el>(καθ-υπέρτερος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a> from <a href='S:καθύπερθε'><el>καθύπερθε</el></a>\n<p/><i>above</i>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>having the upper hand, superior</i>, <el>κ. γίγνεσθαι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>πόλις κ. τῶν ἀντιπάλων</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>καθυπέρτερον</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, = <a href='S:καθύπερθε'><el>καθύπερθε</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}